Audio assets for Word Chain game.
Place the following MP3 files in this directory:

  bgm.mp3         – looping background music (~30s seamless loop, <1MB)
  timer.mp3       – tension-building timer loop (~10s seamless loop, <500KB)
  times-up.mp3    – time's up sting (<100KB)
  skipped.mp3     – skip sound effect (<50KB)
  eliminated.mp3  – elimination sound effect (<100KB)
  passed.mp3      – passed/confirmed chime (<50KB)

IMPORTANT: bgm.mp3 and timer.mp3 MUST be encoded with seamless loop points
(no audible click or amplitude discontinuity at the loop boundary).
The Web Audio API will gaplessly repeat the buffer, but source-file
artifacts will be audible.

Missing files are handled gracefully — the AudioEngine logs a warning
once per missing asset and continues silently.
